{"tid":1849241,"cid":31,"subCid":7,"title":"「新手改歌」武漢肺炎的主題曲","createTime":"2020-01-29T02:54:43.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-18T13:53:46.000Z","uid":71508,"like":3,"dislike":53,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"53b7dec0f310f7914e3ff25d4c4ee75a3f10998c","tid":1849241,"uid":71508,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T02:54:43.000Z","msg":"中國唯一的秘密，武漢最強病毒。<br />\n病毒朋友，佢夠西利，傳染力極高。<br />\n世界第一，非常毒，將所有人染病。<br />\n佢確係勁，哪怕死亡，毒撚馬上消失。<br />\n護衛香港，挽救地球，看守這自由。<br />\n這進行曲一高奏，毒撚便逃走。<br />\n連衞兵，連衞兵，東一隻，西一隻，<br />\n東一腳，西一腳，給批鬥，<br />\n抱鍵盤退後，十秒便失手。"},{"pid":"364781274ea2359cded95aaaf6ec476dce8379fb","tid":1849241,"uid":71508,"like":0,"dislike":7,"score":-7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T02:55:27.000Z","msg":"你地唔使咁快比正評<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我都知我好勁<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fbc0d61a0168bd3b4ebe9b990d00fb7f87ef4d9b","tid":1849241,"uid":44160,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T02:56:20.000Z","msg":"Which church are you from?"},{"pid":"adda739d911b38840b6633e69461e3f975beb502","tid":1849241,"uid":71508,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"fbc0d61a0168bd3b4ebe9b990d00fb7f87ef4d9b","tid":1849241,"uid":44160,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T02:56:20.000Z","msg":"Which church are you from?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T03:06:33.000Z","msg":"Wuhan"},{"pid":"e3f91db05045b2c819666e1ac53511097280844d","tid":1849241,"uid":58209,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T03:14:20.000Z","msg":"武漢唯一的秘密<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/clown4.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"333cba3f95cb62c333d05013ac7e582ed7449805","tid":1849241,"uid":264396,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T03:51:02.000Z","msg":"邊間教會<img src=\"/assets/fa